posting_body: ['Paceline', '17202 Aurora Ave North, Shoreline, WA, 98133', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 7', 'OR Text', '7', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'At Your Own Pace', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 577 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'We believe in doing things at our own pace.', 'So whether you want to spend your night kicking back and relaxing—while watching a live concert from the comfort of our Sky Deck—or throwing a themed party in one of our community lounges, you’ll be right at home.', 'Features', '- Incredible floor to ceiling windows', '- Stylish two tone cabinets to suit a variety of tastes', '- Quality quartz countertops', '- Full kitchen package with stainless steel appliances', 'Community Amenities', '- Free UBER rides Travel in style', '- Pet spa Perfect for pampering your furry friend', "- Biker's Paradise Free storage and trail cruisers", '- Exclusive phone app', '- Sky Lounge Games, sunsets, foosball & working space Extra storage', '- Fitness Loft 24/7 state-of-the-art fitness loft', '- Get Creative Find your inner artist in our DIY Room', '- Available in climate controlled locations', 'Pet Policy', 'We adore pets as much as you do!', 'Your furry (or not so furry) family member will love it here as much as you do!', 'Though we love all pets we do have some breed restrictions, give us a call for more info.', 'BVrXt25N']
